 Namatirai Mashona, Chronicle Reporter A KAMATIVI cop who was facing charges of raping his girlfriend’s niece has been acquitted after the 16-year-old girl confessed that she falsely accused him. The girl shocked the court when she claimed she was possessed by a spirit that pushes her to make sexual advances to men and fabricate sexual abuse charges against those who show no interest in her. She said she once falsely implicated her other uncle for rape after he showed no interest in her sexual advances. More to follow…